and ci = ci‚àí1 = ¬∑ ¬∑ ¬∑ = c1 = 0 for some i(1 ‚â§ i ‚â§ n ‚àí 2). Then ps(n ‚àí j) =
j + 1(1 ‚â§ j ‚â§ i).
