of all possible alternating action streams iasa1,a2 : ‚àÜ‚Üí Actsa1 ‚à™Actsa2 , so that
the following statements hold, for any iasa1,a2 ‚àà Ias‚àÜa1,a2 :‚àí if t is the least time at which iasa1,a2(t)‚Üì then iasa1,a2(t) = asa2(t) (that
is, any alternating action stream initiates with a client request);
‚àí in any alternating action stream iasa1,a2 ‚àà Iasa1,a2 , if at t and t‚Ä≤ there
are iasa1,a2(t) = asa2(t) and iasa1,a2(t
