the server‚Äôs response is coherent with the (generalized) client‚Äôs request.
Ias‚àÜa1,a2 is said to be the generalized alternating action stream underlying the
service scheme Srv‚àÜa1,a2 . We say that the agent a1 performs the service scheme
Srv‚àÜa1,a2 for a2. Also, we say that the interactive system composed of the agents
a1 and (all agents represented by) a2 realizes the service scheme Srv‚àÜa1,a2 .
