that the following notion is trivial for t = ‚ä•.
Definition 3 (t-invariance). Let M = „ÄàS, g, v„Äâ and M‚Ä≤ = „ÄàS‚Ä≤, g‚Ä≤, v‚Ä≤„Äâ be H-
models for LH
