{H0,H1,H2, . . .} is an indexed family which is a superclass of {L0, L1, L2, . . .}.
LetM be a learner for {L0, L1, L2, . . .} with respect to {H0,H1,H2, . . .}. Letmn
be the first index output byM on the canonical text Tn for Ln such thatmn ‚àà In
(mn may not always be defined). Then the set {mn : n ‚àà N and mn exists} is
