Sign ¬¨A A ‚à®B A ‚àßB A ‚äÉ B
Value [0, 1) \A A ‚à™B A ‚à©B ¬¨A ‚à™B
[Nagy 2005b] and used also in [Nagy‚ÄìVa¬¥lyi 2008]. For the completeness of this
paper we recall the definition of product:
Let A =
k‚ãÉ
