of Free Projective Planes
Nurlan Kogabaev
Sobolev Institute of Mathematics
Koptyug Prospect 4, Novosibirsk 630090, Russia.
kogabaev@math.nsc.ru
Shirshov (cf. [1]) suggested to treat projective planes as partial algebraic
